data.description: Prime location! Great home within a Cul-de-Sac. Don't miss out. This rambler offers 4 bed, 3 bath and a fully finished basement. Areas in basement could offer more bedrooms if needed. The home offers excellent storage space with an extra deep garage, a nice storage shed and RV parking. The covered back porch is a great place to gather and is equipped with a 220 outlet for your hot tub or any future needs. The home has new laminate flooring upstairs, new lighting, and is waiting for your final touches.
